details.sectionContent: If capturing your imagination and showing the best of it is what you are interested in then this is the place where you meet your goal. Capture props around you, get the best from it and move to the next level.
Seminar will be conducted. The knowledge on photography art will be presented.
The participants will be instructed to click their best inside the campus, with no theme and submit it.
Participants will be given a theme.  -Theme based photography they have to perform. e.g.- Happiness beyond calculation. Silent communication
